  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndroidMessageKey
    Represents the key of an Android message, in which various bits of data are encoded (name, plural form, array index, etc...).
    AndroidStrings
    A message catalog capable of reading a writing Android strings.xml files.
    FormattedMessage
    A message supporting Formatter-like placeholders.
    MacMessage
    Represents a message in an Apple .strings file.
    MacStrings
    Represents an Apple .strings file.
    ToStringFragmentVisitor
    Implementation of MessageFragmentVisitor that is able to return a string representation of the message it visits.
    ToStringVisitor  
    YamlMessage
    Represents a message in a YAML file.
    YamlStrings
    Represents a set of messages in a YAML file.
